modules.description: Provides functions to initiate barcode scanning, decode scanned data, and handle scan results with custom configurations. Works with string-based scan results and timeout settings. Used to integrate real-time product identification in mobile inventory systems and receipt processing workflows.

Provides functions to encode text into specific formats for barcodes, including email, SMS, phone numbers, and general text. Processes barcode scan results to extract text, format, and cancellation status. Used to initiate scans and generate encoded strings for integration with mobile barcode scanning APIs.
